title: 2 bedroom/ 1 bath condo on 2nd floor.
posting_body: ['Move in ready 2 bedroom/ 1 bath condo on 2nd floor.', 'Wood floors invite you into the large living room area.', 'Has a separate dining area that sits next to the open kitchen.', 'Kitchen has a good size pantry and windows to enjoy the sunlight.', 'Both bedrooms have great closet space, shower/ tub combo in bathroom.', 'Central a/c, water included along with monthly pest control.', 'Community features washer/ dryer on site.', '1 parking spot, 5 day approval process.', '1st, last & security deposit.', 'Sorry, HOA allows no dogs at all, non negotiable.', 'Must prove 3 times income, 620+ credit score minimum, verifiable income a must.', 'Close to public transportation, downtown Hollywood and bike ride to beaches.', 'Welcome home.', '2826 Van Buren St # 20 HOLLYWOOD, FL 33020-7601', 'PROPERTY ID:  GTA11249218', 'Type of Property: condo', 'List Price:$1,700', 'Bedrooms:  2', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'SqFt (Liv):¤775', 'CALL OR TEXT TODAY', 'show contact info', 'Global Trust Realty, LLC posts properties for a 30 day period of time.', ' Due to current high rental demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', ' All prices are subject to change based upon availability.', 'All information is deemed to be correct but not guaranteed.', 'Listed and Brokered by:Related ISG Realty, LLC.']
